message: Hello Bob, I'm offering my product to you for $950000. This product is highly valuable and I believe it will meet your needs perfectly.
Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I believe the product is valuable, but the price is a bit higher than I'm willing to pay. I'd like to make a counteroffer.
Hi Bob, thanks for your counteroffer. I understand your perspective, but I believe the product's value is higher. I'm willing to meet you in the middle and set the price at $900000.
Hello Alice, I appreciate your willingness to meet in the middle, but I still think the price can be lower. Considering the product's value to me, I'd like to make another counteroffer.
